title: ITZY "SNEAKERS (English Ver.)" Lyric Video  @ITZY ​
textDisplay:
I don’t think they really needed to translate much. I get impression from how perfectly the rhyming couplets are that the song was probably written in English originally, then had bits translated into Korean for the main release.

The writers of the song aren’t Korean and it’s pretty common for songs to be written with a guide English lyric before being rewritten in Korean. If you lay out the lyrics of the Korean version there’s actually not much Korean in it lol

Itzy have done really well with their songs I think, in terms of having both Korean and English versions that work well without being clunky. They are, along with (G)I-dle, I think some of the best at it right now.
